hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm training to be an engineer medibenefits.com I fell in love with Germany as a teenager. While others found the language difficult, I loved its crisp sound and orderly structure. Staying with my German penpal in Munich, I discovered wheat beer and the fairytale woodlands and mountains of Bavaria. When I visited Berlin for the first time, there were still artists squatting in ruined buildings in the city centre; it seemed the anarchic flipside of competitive London.
